Document: VisualShaderNodeTexture2DArrayParameter
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodetexture2darrayparameter.rst
Summary: This parameter provides a collection of textures for shaders, with the VisualShaderNodeTexture2DArray node used to extract individual textures from the array.

This parameter allows to provide a collection of textures for the shader. You can use VisualShaderNodeTexture2DArray to extract the textures from array.